'''Republic crewmen''' were the enlisted units of the [[Republic Navy/Legends|Republic Navy]], serving as navigators, surveyors and operators of each individual [[Starship/Legends|starship]]. They were the naval equivalent of the [[Republic Army|army's]] [[Republic soldier|soldiers]].

